UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The discovery of the Rosetta Stone, a large slab of black granite inscribed with three different scripts, was a major breakthrough in the study of ancient Egyptian hieroglyphs.  Because the stone contained the same decree written in Greek, Demotic script, and hieroglyphs, scholars could compare the texts and decipher the hieroglyphs for the first time. What is the most likely reason why the Rosetta Stone was so important?',
