  stimulus_text = 'The article discusses a new study suggesting that the most effective way to teach young children a new language is through songs.  The author argues that songs are more effective than traditional methods of teaching new languages, such as flashcards or worksheets.  The author also argues that songs help to make learning a new language more enjoyable for children, making the process more engaging and effective.  The author concludes by suggesting that this approach could be used to teach other subjects as well.',
