  stimulus_text = 'The development of artificial intelligence, or AI, has progressed quickly in recent decades. With the availability of large amounts of data and powerful computers, AI is being used to do a variety of tasks that were once thought to be impossible for machines. AI is now being used to automate tasks such as driving cars, translating languages, and writing articles. Some experts believe that AI will eventually surpass human intelligence, while others are more cautious. The potential benefits of AI are significant, but so are the risks.  It is important to think carefully about the potential consequences of AI before it becomes too powerful.',
