  options = '[{"id":"A","text":"People often focus on the tangible aspects of progress at the expense of intangible values.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"The speaker argues that people tend to focus on the tangible aspects of progress, such as new technologies and economic growth, while overlooking the more important intangible values, such as human connection and a sense of community. This is the main problem with the idea of \"progress\" in the moder. Choice A matches the question''s requirement and is consistent with the passage''s central claim or supporting detail. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."},{"id":"B","text":"Progress is always a positive force that leads to a better world for everyone.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice B is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."},{"id":"C","text":"Progress is an impossible ideal that can never be fully achieved.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice C is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."},{"id":"D","text":"Progress is only meaningful if it benefits all members of society.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice D is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."}]'::jsonb,
