  stimulus_text = 'The passage describes a study that was conducted to evaluate the effectiveness of a new drug in treating a particular type of cancer. The study involved a control group of patients who did not receive the drug, and a treatment group of patients who did. The study found that the treatment group had a significantly lower rate of tumor growth than the control group. However, the study also found that the treatment group experienced a higher rate of side effects than the control group. The researchers concluded that the drug was effective in slowing tumor growth, but they also recommended that further research be conducted to better understand the potential side effects of the drug.',
  question_text = 'Which of the following is the most likely reason why the researchers recommended further research?',
  stimulus_type = NULL,
